data.description: *****Motivated Seller*****  This hidden gem in the woods is the get-away you are looking for.   This 3 bedroom 2 bath home is nestled under tall trees with a fully fenced in lot. There is a semi-circle drive behind gates that are manually operated and you will love the beauty of God's creation every time you step outside.  The potential in this wonderful home is one that will be hard to pass up.
